# Data Protection Policy

## Purpose
To ensure the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of company data.

## Data Handling Guidelines
- All sensitive data must be encrypted during storage and transmission.
- Regular audits of data access should be conducted.
- Employees must sign non-disclosure agreements before accessing sensitive data.

## Consequences of Non-Compliance
Failure to follow this policy may result in legal action, loss of access to sensitive data, or disciplinary actions.
